content: This is so awesome. You have no idea how many guys I talk to who wish they had this with their sons. With AI, we could both be huge. The only thing I would change is adding like a leadership component where he learns about greats and reads, like Elon, Marcus Aurelius, also like Jocko and Tim Ferriss. I think he’d be so sweet with that upbringing. Am I wrong? Like if he has AI to support before everyone else catches on, I think there is no better way to get ahead in life. And he has so much going for him with his environment
